OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778073067
OL,3,CTeacher accused of murdering baby
OL,4,Cbegged medics 'don't let him die',
OL,5,Ccourt hears
OL,7,FA teacher accused of the abuse and
OL,8,Fmurder of a baby he adopted with his
OL,9,Fpartner begged medics "don't let him
OL,10,Fdie," a court heard.
OL,12,FJamie Varley, 37, rushed 13-month-old
OL,13,FPreston Davey to Blackpool Victoria
OL,14,FHospital unconscious in his arms, a
OL,15,Fjury at Preston Crown Court has been
OL,16,Ftold.
OL,26,@qD@WOUrD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
