OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778073067
OL,3,CTeacher accused of murdering baby
OL,4,Cbegged medics 'don't let him die',
OL,5,Ccourt hears
OL,7,FMedics worked for nearly an hour to
OL,8,Fresuscitate the child until a decision
OL,9,Fwas made that further intervention was
OL,10,Ffutile and life was pronounced extinct
OL,11,Fat 7.18pm on July 27, 2023.
OL,13,FVarley, at the time a high school
OL,14,Fteacher, is accused of the murder of
OL,15,Fthe child and his partner, John
OL,16,FMcGowan-Fazakerley, 32, of allowing
OL,17,Fthe death of the child, with both
OL,18,Faccused of sexual abuse.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778073067
OL,3,CTeacher accused of murdering baby
OL,4,Cbegged medics 'don't let him die',
OL,5,Ccourt hears
OL,7,FDuring the four months the baby was
OL,8,Funder their adoption at their home in
OL,9,FBlackpool, he was allegedly routinely
OL,10,Fill-treated, had indecent images and
OL,11,Fvideos taken of him, was sexually
OL,12,Fabused and physically assaulted, with
OL,13,Fa post-mortem examination identifying
OL,14,F40 injuries, jurors have heard.
OL,16,FOn the day Preston died, at around
OL,17,F6.25pm, paramedic Simon Crabb was
OL,18,Foutside the ambulance bay and saw
OL,19,FVarley running with a "floppy" baby in
OL,20,Fhis arms, and told him the child was
OL,21,Fnot breathing.
OL,26,@{D@WOU{D@^O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
