OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778073067
OL,3,CTeacher accused of murdering baby
OL,4,Cbegged medics 'don't let him die',
OL,5,Ccourt hears
OL,7,FMr Crabb said the other parent was
OL,8,Fpresent and was calmer, "but had a
OL,9,Flook of terror in his eyes".
OL,11,FHe took the child and began giving
OL,12,Fmouth-to-mouth rescue breaths as he
OL,13,Fran inside the Accident and Emergency
OL,14,FDepartment and a "crash" team was
OL,15,Fscrambled.
OL,17,FPreston was given chest compressions
OL,18,Fand oxygen, while other medics rushed
OL,19,Fto help and specialist equipment
OL,20,Freadied.
OL,26,@pD@YOUqD@[O]vD@ROUvD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
