OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778073067
OL,3,CTeacher accused of murdering baby
OL,4,Cbegged medics 'don't let him die',
OL,5,Ccourt hears
OL,7,FMr Crabb said Varley was "hysterical"
OL,8,Fand told him he had left the baby in
OL,9,Fthe bath while he had a shower and
OL,10,Freturned three to four minutes later.
OL,12,FMr Crabb said Varley told him: "Don't
OL,13,Flet him die! Please don't let him die."
OL,15,FAn emergency team worked for up to an
OL,16,Fhour on the child but he could not be
OL,17,Frevived, the court heard.
OL,26,@oD@ZOUoD@eO]tD@`OUuD@gO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
