PN,39706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778073067
OL,3,CTeacher accused of murdering baby
OL,4,Cbegged medics 'don't let him die',
OL,5,Ccourt hears
OL,7,FDr Wendy Aubrey, a senior
OL,8,Fanaesthetist, had intubated Preston `
OL,9,Fthat is inserted a small tube into his
OL,10,Fthroat to get oxygen to his lungs.
OL,12,FShe told the jury she did not see any
OL,13,Fwater in the child's mouth or airways,
OL,14,Fadding: "There was no water in his
OL,15,Flungs. I would have expected water in
OL,16,Fhis lungs."
OL,26,@vD@IOUxD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
