OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778073067
OL,3,CTeacher accused of murdering baby
OL,4,Cbegged medics 'don't let him die',
OL,5,Ccourt hears
OL,7,FShe said it was standard practice to
OL,8,Finvite family in to see their child
OL,9,Funder resuscitation and both
OL,10,Fdefendants and Varley's mother were
OL,11,Fbrought in to see Preston.
OL,13,FDr Aubrey continued: "I recall one dad
OL,14,Fquite subdued.
OL,16,F"The other dad was very dramatic and
OL,17,Fmore dramatic than I have seen parents
OL,18,Fpreviously. A bit chaotic. He would
OL,19,Fnot stand still and let people support
OL,20,Fhim and would not listen to what has
OL,21,Fbeen said.
OL,26,@uD@VOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778073067
OL,3,CTeacher accused of murdering baby
OL,4,Cbegged medics 'don't let him die',
OL,5,Ccourt hears
OL,7,F"He was initially shouting, 'Don't let
OL,8,Fhim die.' He said, 'I effing killed
OL,9,Fhim.'"
OL,11,FAfter efforts to revive Preston had
OL,12,Fended, Dr Aubrey said the same parent,
OL,13,Fidentified in the medical notes as
OL,14,FVarley, then tried to give chest
OL,15,Fcompressions and mouth to mouth
OL,16,Fresuscitation to Preston, despite the
OL,17,Fbreathing tube being still in place.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
