FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778073067
OL,3,CTeacher accused of murdering baby
OL,4,Cbegged medics 'don't let him die',
OL,5,Ccourt hears
OL,7,FShe added: "I had to be really quite
OL,8,Ffirm and tell him to stop because of
OL,9,Fwhat he was continuing trying to do to
OL,10,FPreston."
OL,12,FDr Anthony Kearns, lead consultant in
OL,13,Fthe accident and emergency department
OL,14,Fwho tried to save Preston, said he had
OL,15,Fbeen told the child had been pulled
OL,16,Ffrom water.
OL,18,FDr Kearns continued: "The child was
OL,19,Fcompletely dry. They had a nappy in
OL,20,Fsitu, which appeared to be
OL,21,Fappropriately placed."
OL,26,@oD@LOUrD@IO]zD@VOU}D@VO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
