PN,39710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778073067
OL,3,CTeacher accused of murdering baby
OL,4,Cbegged medics 'don't let him die',
OL,5,Ccourt hears
OL,7,FFour hours before the hospital visit,
OL,8,FVarley had visited his mother's house.
OL,10,FJurors were shown a video clip he had
OL,11,Ftaken and sent to his co-accused, who
OL,12,Fwas at work, of Preston being bounced
OL,13,Fon his grandmother's knee.
OL,15,FShe is singing, "If you're happy and
OL,16,Fyou know it clap you're your hands"
OL,17,Fwith Preston smiling and clapping his
OL,18,Fhands along to the song.
OL,26,@wD@QOUxD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
