OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778073067
OL,3,CTeacher accused of murdering baby
OL,4,Cbegged medics 'don't let him die',
OL,5,Ccourt hears
OL,7,FIt is alleged after leaving her house
OL,8,Fto go home Varley subjected the child
OL,9,Fto a final sexual assault.
OL,11,FVarley denies murder, manslaughter,
OL,12,Ftwo counts of assault by penetration,
OL,13,Ffive counts of cruelty to a child,
OL,14,Fgrievous bodily harm, sexual assault
OL,15,Fof a child, 13 counts of taking
OL,16,Findecent photos or videos of a child,
OL,17,Fone of distributing an indecent photo
OL,18,Fof a child, to his co-accused, and one
OL,19,Fof making an indecent photo.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
