CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778073067
OL,3,CTeacher accused of murdering baby
OL,4,Cbegged medics 'don't let him die',
OL,5,Ccourt hears
OL,7,FMcGowan-Fazakerley denies allowing the
OL,8,Fdeath of a child, three counts of
OL,9,Fchild cruelty and one count of the
OL,10,Fsexual assault of a child.
OL,12,FThe trial was adjourned until
OL,13,FWednesday morning.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/12
